high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the glass coffee table.
Pick up the credit card from the edge of the coffee table.
Walk closer to the middle of the coffee table.
Place the credit card on the white plate on the table.
Pick up the white plate from the table.
Walk to the couch to the right of the table, then to the end table to the left of the couch.
Place the plate on the end table.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a credit card on it on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left and walk forward and turn left to face the living room table.
Pick up the card on the living room table.
Take a step to the right and face the card on the plate on the living room table.
Take a step to the right and place the card on the plate on the living room table.
Pick up the plate with the car on it on the table.
Walk around the right side of the table and walk across the room, then turn left and walk forward to face the end table to the left of the couch.
Place the plate with the card on it on the end table.
anns.task_desc: To put a card on a plate and move them to the end table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the chair, then hang a left and walk up to the glass coffee table.
Pick up the leftmost credit card off of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the glass coffee table.
Put the credit card on the white plate that is on the coffee table.
Pick up the white plate with the credit card on it off of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk around the coffee table to the black shelving unit that is to the left of the couch.
Put the white plate with the credit card on it on top of the black shelving unit to the right of the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Put a white plate with a credit card on it on top of a black shelving unit.
